{"TopicId":108281,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"\u0026#039;Couple questions...","CreatedByName":"Templar","CreatedById":142441,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-08T21:21:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Templar","CreatedById":142441,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-08T21:21:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022Is it impossible for one to close their own threads..?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003ECan I create a thread for a company although I don\u0027t have any partners?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022How does one become a moderator?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022Is there a place on the forums where all of this information is already located?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003EThanks\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gaarst","CreatedById":126740,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-08T21:50:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYes, a moderator can.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou don\u0027t.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYes, \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/30064-Community-Rules-July-24-2014\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"technicalfool","CreatedById":70430,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-08T22:17:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Templar\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Templar\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022Is it impossible for one to close their own threads..?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYes, but you can use \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/25176\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethe request thread\u003C/a\u003E, or use the Report Post feature.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Templar\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Templar\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003ECan I create a thread for a company although I don\u0027t have any partners?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENot sure on the convention for rocket company threads. I\u0027m not often on that bit of the forums.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Templar\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Templar\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022How does one become a moderator?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKeep your eyes on the Announcements or Daily Kerbal subforum and wait for someone like Kaspervld or the SQUAD account to ask for moderator applications.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBe aware though, the job may not be what you think it is. It\u0027s a lot less of this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17qgo22anjpxcjpg/original.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022original.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Csup\u003E\u003Cem\u003EJudge Dredd\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/sup\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd a lot more of this:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://images1.fanpop.com/images/photos/1600000/the-janitor-moments-the-janitor-1671883-576-432.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022the-janitor-moments-the-janitor-1671883-576-432.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Csup\u003E\u003Cem\u003EJanitor\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/sup\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Templar\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Templar\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003E\u0022Is there a place on the forums where all of this information is already located?\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENot really, though you can use the forum search function or Google.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Templar\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Templar\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Consolas;\u0022\u003EThanks\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYer welcome!\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-05-08T22:39:50Z\u0022 title=\u002205/08/2015 10:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EMay 8, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by technicalfool\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xannari Ferrows","CreatedById":125369,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-08T22:44:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022technicalfool\u0022 data-cite=\u0022technicalfool\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EBe aware though, the job may not be what you think it is. It\u0027s a lot less of this:\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/17qgo22anjpxcjpg/original.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022ext